{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "superplane-oncall",
  "title": "SuperPlane - AI On-Call Agent",
  "tags": ["superplane", "oncall"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Agent Status",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "up{job=\"superplane-agent\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Agent"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" }, "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "green", "value": 1 }]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Prometheus Status",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "up{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" }, "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "green", "value": 1 }]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Targets Up/Down",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "up",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Trigger AI Investigation",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Manually Trigger Investigation\n\nSend a POST request to the AI agent:\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3001/agent/investigate \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"alert\": {\n      \"service\": \"payment-service\",\n      \"severity\": \"critical\",\n      \"message\": \"High error rate detected\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"'$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)'\"\n    }\n  }'\n```\n\n**Available services:** `payment-service`, `api-gateway`, `user-service`\n\n**Severity levels:** `critical`, `high`, `medium`, `low`\n\n---\n\n**Agent URL:** [http://localhost:3001](http://localhost:3001)\n\n**Health check:** [http://localhost:3001/health](http://localhost:3001/health)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Prometheus Scrape Duration",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "scrape_duration_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
